data.description: Welcome to 1423 Fawn Lily Drive! This Stunning 2726 sq ft Temple, Texas home is the perfect place for you and yours. You'll love the gorgeous new floors, updated roof, and extended fence for added privacy. The kitchen boasts granite countertops and an island, perfect for whipping up homemade meals. Enjoy a cozy evening in the living room with a warm fireplace in the winter or step out onto the covered patio and BBQ in the Summer– there's no shortage of amenities here! Lifestyle wise you're close to local shops, dining, recreation, and parks. With 4 bedrooms, an office Second Living Area Upstairs with a Wood Privacy screen, and 3 full bathrooms, there's plenty of space for everyone to spread out. Don't wait - book a viewing today!
